	(1, 'technical-hiring', 'Technical Hiring Services', 'Great tech starts with great minds. RaremindsΓÇÖ Technical Hiring Services match you with top-tier talent that powers innovation and builds the future of your business.', 'Book a Call', 'https://itvhjkgfafikpqmuunlh.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/images/Corporate/Recruitment/service/Technical-Hiring.webp', 'Diverse business professionals collaborating on colorful abstract data cloud', 'Rareminds Building Winning Tech Teams with Confidence', '["Technical human resources play a crucial role in building digital products, modernizing infrastructure, all of which are a plethora of options that can be used for scaling globally. Tech is a catalyst for scaling businesses, and having the right tech minds on board directly impacts your business outcomes.", "Rareminds'' specialized Technical Hiring Services are built to meet the complex demands of modern tech recruitment, combining speed, accuracy, and deep domain expertise to help you hire with confidence."]', 'What Does Our Technical Hiring Services Deliver?', 'At Rareminds, we specialize in identifying talent that fits seamlessly with your business culture, goals, and technical requirements.', '[{"t_1": "Precision", "t_2": "Tech Hiring", "points": ["Deep-dive assessments through coding tests, live problem-solving, and system design interviews.", "Specialized recruitment across domains like software, DevOps, cloud, AI/ML, data science, and cybersecurity.", "Focused on aligning tech skills with real business needs."]}, {"t_1": "Speed", "t_2": "Meets Scale", "points": ["Agile, fast-track hiring workflows for startups, SMEs, and enterprises.", "Scalable support for single-role or bulk tech hiring.", "Reduced time-to-hire with a streamlined recruitment engine."]}, {"t_1": "Elite Talent Access", "t_2": "and Experience", "points": ["Curated access to both active and hard-to-reach passive candidates.", "Personalized engagement and outreach strategies to attract top talent